## Welcome to my site
> Curiouser and curiouser!‚Äù Cried Alice (she was so much surprised, that for the moment she quite forgot how to speak good English).
What did Duchamp mean by creating *Fountain*? How are we desensitized by different images? How many television ads does the average person watch in a year? What do cats and catapults have in common?

On this site, join a student who is starting to question her world.
